{"title":"MOD Police Committee","public_updated_at":"2017-01-19T13:46:07Z","details":{"email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The <abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr> Police Committee is an associate member of the Association of Police and Crime Commissioners (APCC), and mirrors policing governance best practice where possible and appropriate.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"meeting-minutes\">Meeting minutes</h2>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907512\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583562/1-modpcmins_20151208.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 8 December 2015</a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">41KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907511\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583561/2-20151001-MODPC_Sep_15-Minutes.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 1 September 2015</a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">58.6KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907510\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583560/3-20150527-MODPC_May_15-Minutes-FOI_Pub.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 12 May 2015 </a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">64.6KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907508\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583559/4-20150227-MODPC_Feb_15-Minutes-FOI_Pub.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 10 February 2015</a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">35.1KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907507\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583557/5-20140902_MODPC_Sep14_Minutes.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 2 September 2014</a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">40.1KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907506\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583555/6-20140708_MODPC_Jun14_Minutes.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 2 June 2014 </a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">32.1KB</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907504\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583554/7-20140604-modpc-minutes-jun-2014.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 4 February 2014</a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">36.5KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">7 pages</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907500\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583552/8-mod_pc_mins_nov13.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 5 November 2013 </a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">48.1KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">9 pages</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907499\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n<a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/583551/9-modpcmins_20130713.pdf\">MODPC: meeting minutes 30 July 2013 </a>\n(<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">63.1KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">9 pages</span>)\n</span></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><span id=\"attachment_1907498\" class=\"attachmen